	<h4 style="text-align: center;">4 CULTURE - "Promoting Culture Through Partnerships"</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>A Partnership of four of Sault Ste. Marie’s Favourite Attractions</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>&nbsp;</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Sault Ste. Marie Museum</em><br /><em>Art Gallery of Algoma</em><br /><em>Ermatinger • Clergue National Historic Site</em><br /><em>Canadian Bushplane Heritage Centre</em><br /><br /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="vertical-align: middle;" src="images/4Culture.jpg" alt="" width="235" height="314" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Buy a Passport and Get Cultural !!!!<br /><br /></h4>
<p style="text-align: center;">4Culture offers a Passport which provides admission to all four sites for one low price. The Passport saves the visitor approximately 48% of their admission fees.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br />Cost – Adult (18 years &amp; older) $25<br /> Student / Child (12 to 17) $10</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Passports can be purchased at any of the four attractions. There is no expiration date and can be used at any time.</p>
